<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@themesberg/flowbite@1.2.0/dist/flowbite.min.css" />





    <div class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-4">
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap -mb-px" id="myTab" data-tabs-toggle="#myTabContent" role="tablist">
            <li class="mr-2" role="presentation">
            <%= button_tag class: "inline-block text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 hover:border-gray-300 rounded-t-lg py-4 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-center border-transparent border-b-2 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-300 active", id: "new-tab", "data-tabs-target": "#new", type: "button", role: "tab", "aria-controls": "profile", "aria-selected": true do %>
                New VPN
            <% end %>
            </li>
            <li class="mr-2" role="presentation">
            <%= button_tag class: "inline-block text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 hover:border-gray-300 rounded-t-lg py-4 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-center border-transparent border-b-2 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-300", id: "deploy-tab", "data-tabs-target": "#deploy", type: "button", role: "tab", "aria-controls": "dashboard", "aria-selected": false do %>
                Deploy VPN
            <% end %>
            </li>
            <li class="mr-2" role="presentation">
            <%= button_tag class: "inline-block text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 hover:border-gray-300 rounded-t-lg py-4 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-center border-transparent border-b-2 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-300", id: "help-tab", "data-tabs-target": "#help", type: "button", role: "tab", "aria-controls": "settings", "aria-selected": false do %>
            Help
            <% end %>
            </li>
            <li role="presentation">
            <%= button_tag class: "inline-block text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 hover:border-gray-300 rounded-t-lg py-4 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-center border-transparent border-b-2 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-300", id: "faq-tab", "data-tabs-target": "#faq", type: "button", role: "tab", "aria-controls": "contacts", "aria-selected": false do %>
            FAQ
            <% end %>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="myTabContent">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg dark:bg-gray-800" id="new" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="profile-tab">
        <%= form_with(model: @vpn, local: true, url: create_vpn_path, method: :post) do |form| %>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full  px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <%= form.label :name, class: "block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2 parse" do %>
                        Name
                    <% end %>
                    <%= form.text_field :name, name: "vpn[name]", id: "vpn_name", class: "appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 border border-red-500 rounded py-3 px-4 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white" %>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                        <label for="vpn_description" class="block mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                            Description
                        </label>
                        <%= form.text_area :description, id: "vpn_description", rows: 4, class: "block p-2.5 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-blue-500 dark:focus:border-blue-500", placeholder: "Write your thoughts here..." %>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3">
                        <label class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" for="vpn_password">
                            Password
                        </label>
                        <%= form.password_field :password, id: "vpn_password",name: "vpn[password]", class: "appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 border border-gray-200 rounded py-3 px-4 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500", style: "display: none;" %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center h-5">
                        <%= form.check_box :use_password, id: "vpn_use_password", class: "w-4 h-4 border border-gray-300 rounded bg-gray-50 focus:ring-3 focus:ring-blue-300 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:focus:ring-blue-600 dark:ring-offset-gray-800 dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-800", onclick: "document.getElementById('vpn_password').style.display = (this.checked ? 'inline' : 'none');" %>
                    </div>
                    <label for="terms" class="ml-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300">Select this if you want to use a password</label>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                        <%= form.label :port, class: "block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" do %>
                            Port
                        <% end %>
                        <%= form.text_field :port, name: "vpn[port]",class: "appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 border border-gray-200 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500" %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                        <%= form.label :server, class: "block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" do %>
                            Server
                        <% end %>
                        <%= form.text_field :server,name: "vpn[server]", class: "appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 border border-gray-200 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500" %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <%= form.label :technology, class: "block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2" do %>
                        Technology
                      <% end %>
                      <%= form.text_field :technology, class: "appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 border border-gray-200 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight", readonly: true, value: "OpenVPN" %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <%= form.label :users, class: "block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2", for: "users" do %>
                        Select users
                      <% end %>
                      <%= form.select :users, options_for_select(["Choose users", "Example1", "Example2", "Example3", "Example4"]), class: "block appearance-none w-full bg-gray-200 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 py-3 px-4 pr-8 rounded leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500", id: "users" %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <%= form.label :administrators, class: "block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2", for: "administrators" do %>
                        Select administrators
                      <% end %>
                      <%= form.select :administrators, options_for_select(["Choose administrators", "Example1", "Example2", "Example3", "Example4"]), class: "block appearance-none w-full bg-gray-200 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 py-3 px-4 pr-8 rounded leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500", id: "administrators" %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-full px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                        <label for="Bandwidth" class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2">Limit bandwidth</label>
                        <%= form.select :bandwidth, options_for_select([['Choose bandwidth(MB/s)', ''], ['5', 5], ['10', 10], ['25', 25], ['50', 50], ['75', 75], ['100', 100]]), { include_blank: true }, class: 'block appearance-none w-full bg-gray-200 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 py-3 px-4 pr-8 rounded leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500', id: 'bandwidth' %>

                    </div>
                </div>
                </br>
               <%= form.submit "Create VPN", class: "text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 text-center dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800" %> 
        </div>

        <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg dark:bg-gray-800 hidden" id="deploy" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="dashboard-tab">
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">This is some placeholder content the <strong class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Dashboard tab's associated content</strong>. Clicking another tab will toggle the visibility of this one for the next. The tab JavaScript swaps classes to control the content visibility and styling.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg dark:bg-gray-800 hidden" id="help" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="settings-tab">

        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg dark:bg-gray-800 hidden" id="faq" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="contacts-tab">
            <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-open border border-base-300 bg-base-100 rounded-box my-5">
                <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
                    How can I monitore a VPN?
                </div>
                <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p>You are only allowed to monitore a VPN if the signed user has an administrator role of it, there is an exceptional case, if the user is the global
                    administrator is able to monitore every single network. When one of these conditions have been accomplished, user can click at the home window the monitore
                    button of the VPN selected.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-open border border-base-300 bg-base-100 rounded-box my-5">
            <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
                How can I create a VPN?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content">
                <p>Every user is allowed to create a VPN. In the VPN window, user is automatically redirected to the VPN creation site, then user has to fill all the gaps in
                order to create the VPN desired.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>       
    </div>

</div>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/@themesberg/flowbite@1.2.0/dist/flowbite.bundle.js"></script>
